SQAO.Name: Square One 1.0
SQAO.Message: Built on the Premise that Avara was meant for killing, this Simple Level offers No Escape and Plenty of Carnage.

SQAT.Name: Square Too 1.5
SQAT.Message: Square One with a Few Extras.

SQAH.Name: Square Three 1.0
SQAH.Message: Just another variation on the theme. Watch out for the Hector in the middle.

SQUF.Name: Square Four 1.0
SQUF.Message: Typical Cnemie's Square design with a little less jumping.

SQAF.Name: Square Fin 1.0
SQAF.Message: Add teleporters and a few extras and you get the last of Cnemie's Squares.
